<section>

<para>
All nginx security issues should be reported to
<link url="mailto:security-alert@nginx.org">security-alert@nginx.org</link>.
</para>

<para>
Patches are signed using one of the
<link doc="pgp_keys.xml">PGP public keys</link>.
</para>

